json.text: How do you stay so strong?

Fallen angel, just let go you don’t have to be alone
Fallen angel, close your eyes I won’t let you fall tonight
I was right beside you when you went to hell and back again
I was right beside you when you went to hell and back again
And I, I can save, a fallen angel
